'''亚美尼亚区'''（{{lang-hy|Երուսաղէմի հայկական թաղամաս}}；{{lang-he|הרובע הארמני}}；{{lang-ar|حارة الأرمن}}）是[[耶路撒冷旧城|耶路撒冷旧城]]的四个分区之一，是其中面积最小、人口也最少的一个。

2001年，有2,500名[[亚美尼亚人|亚美尼亚人]]住在耶路撒冷，其中大多数住在位于圣雅各修道院的宗主教区内或附近，宗主教区占据了亚美尼亚区的很大一部分<ref>Jerusalem Post, March 30, 2001 - [http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/71008778.html?dids=71008778:71008778&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Mar+30%2C+2001&author=Patricia+Golan&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=12&desc=A+Cloistered+Community A Cloistered Community] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/71008778.html?dids=71008778:71008778&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Mar+30%2C+2001&author=Patricia+Golan&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=12&desc=A+Cloistered+Community |date=20121022131038 }}</ref><ref>Jerusalem Post, Sept 9, 1993 - [http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/99766520.html?dids=99766520:99766520&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Sep+9%2C+1993&author=HAIM+SHAPIRO&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=14&desc=ARMENIAN+PATRIARCHATE+PLANS+NEW+CONSTRUCTION Armenian Patriarchate Plans New Construction] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/jpost/access/99766520.html?dids=99766520:99766520&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Sep+9%2C+1993&author=HAIM+SHAPIRO&pub=Jerusalem+Post&edition=&startpage=14&desc=ARMENIAN+PATRIARCHATE+PLANS+NEW+CONSTRUCTION |date=20121022131149 }}</ref>。

